Package info.ovhs.robotics.commands.conveyer

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConveyerJoystickControl
    Allows control of conveyer belt with joystick control (Uses Y axis on the operator control
    ConveyerMove
    Moves the conveyer a set direction
    DropTote
    Drops a tote
    Hold
    Keeps the conveyer in the same place (Does not use PID)
    HoldPID
    Uses PID Controller in order to hold tote in one position using the conveyer belt
    LiftTote
    Lifts a tote
    LowerConveyerToBottom
    Lowers the conveyer to the bottom by using the initial Encoder Distance
    ResetConveyer
    Uses a PID Controller to reset the conveyer belt
